      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/marathon-petroleum-mpc-texas-city-orders-residents-to-shelter-in-place</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马拉松石油公司加尔维斯顿湾炼油厂发生化学品泄漏后，得克萨斯州官员要求一些当地居民呆在家里，随后解除了就地避难令。]]></description>
